pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `pokemon` ( `Numero` int(255) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `Miniature` varchar(50) NOT NULL, `Nom` varchar(50) NOT NULL, `Evolution` int(1) NOT NULL, `Type1` int(20) DEFAULT NULL, `Type2` int(20) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`Numero`), KEY `type` (`Type1`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=153 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;
